# Automation Engine — ignore tasks em processamento e logs grandes
.automation-engine/tasks/processing/
.automation-engine/tasks/completed/
.automation-engine/tasks/failed/

# Manter no repositório:
# .automation-engine/AGENT.md          ← motor principal (SEMPRE commitar)
# .automation-engine/QUICK-START.md    ← guia de uso (SEMPRE commitar)
# .automation-engine/config/            ← configurações (SEMPRE commitar)
# .automation-engine/core/              ← regras (SEMPRE commitar)
# .automation-engine/validation/        ← validação (SEMPRE commitar)
# .automation-engine/tasks/incoming/TEMPLATE.task.json  ← template (commitar)
# .automation-engine/logs/execution-log.json  ← depende da equipe
